{"tid":1982710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Chinese-Canadian: \"葉問4講歧視真係好令人反思呀\"","createTime":"2020-04-21T10:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T07:40:17.000Z","uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"59045e5bc69499e632947c9eabe610de45a2747d","tid":1982710,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"有個Chinese-Canadian 佢youtube channel都接近成100k subscribers<br />\n係影評話而家因為疫情比人歧視好驚出街<br />\n原本睇葉問4覺得好普通 依家好多反思wor<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HqmijQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HqmijQ.jpg&h=25b7d916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fNvV6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fNvV6U.jpg&h=6b5cbb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DhvV6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DhvV6C.jpg&h=5bf0fc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW9VnMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW9VnMC.jpg&h=a564b041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/686TTTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F686TTTg.jpg&h=2dcc2730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cObFyh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cObFyh.jpg&h=d21877f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFO3wEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFO3wEY.jpg&h=06309d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成段野又係呢D各打50大板套路<br />\n&quot;邊度都有好人壞人&quot; &quot;我地一齊make the world better啦&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班左膠見到真係丁到出血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打們可以上去正視聽<br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CAFMXrMl23c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCAFMXrMl23c&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=dbab7590\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CAFMXrMl23c</a><br />\n<br />\nAccented Cinema<br />\n@AccentedCinema<br />\nLet's talk about Ip Man 4, a film that I didn't like at first, but grew to appreciate after the world ended... The Ip Man series is no stranger to the theme of racism, but it has never been well done... Until now. Let's see how!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AccentedCinema/status/1250861486135742464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAccentedCinema%2Fstatus%2F1250861486135742464&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=887021c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAccentedCinema%2Fstatus%2F1250861486135742464&h=9f30b1d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AccentedCinema/status/1250861486135742464</a>"},{"pid":"fd4fa1e7d7d3df986f4b43634bb828934a543883","tid":1982710,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"Ip Man itself is a chauvinistic historical-fantasy film series that sets up the straw man of the &quot;evil foreigner&quot; and then destroys it via the proxy of Ip Man acting as the physical manifestation of the Chinese Dream. It's basically our generation's Jud S&uuml;&szlig; (1940), reappropriating history to serve the national fantasy narrative of &quot;My race is better than yours&quot;, it's just that this time the film isn't accusing the Jews for being manipulative, but the Europeans for being racist.<br />\n<br />\nIt's hilarious and sad that you would mistaken this as the opposite, that somehow Ip Man is conductive to anti-racism, when the whole premise of the film is racism itself."},{"pid":"1298ec6fc58f85b33db9f836ce7e5229ad62fa5e","tid":1982710,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4fa1e7d7d3df986f4b43634bb828